				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204880" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;" >DarkStuff</a></span> <span class="odate time_1609262096 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">29 Dec 2020 17:14</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4856759">
									

<p>This was my <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/art-exchange-hub">Art Exchange gift</a> for <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609272431" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span>, who asked for something that starred his character Sasha Merlo. I, however, hit a bit of a brick wall. Having read over a ton of <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/those-twisted-pines-hub">Those Twisted Pines</a> in preparation to write this character, I struggled because&#8230; she's finished! Her backstory is filled in by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609272431" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span>, her frontstory is filled in by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609272431" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span> &#8212; and I mean, that covers her <em>entire life</em>. My first idea was to make a story centered around her husband, Gabe Merlo, but he's pretty developed as well, and has a boring job (no offense), so there wasn't much to do there either.</p>
<p>So I struggled a bit here, and then there, and bit my nails, was like <em>oh no what do I do</em>, until I realized that I had probably write a story about someone <em>else</em> in the canon while having Merlo be an important character in that story. As the tale evolved, Merlo's involvement went down until she had only two scenes (seen here), but&#8230; I couldn't figure out a better way to do it. So, Conwell, I'm sorry that this isn't precisely what you asked for, but I just fell in love with Phineas, and so here he is in all his glory.</p>
<p>Thanks for giving me such an interesting time. I've now read plenty more Twisted Pines than I'd ever read before, and my appreciation for your work has peaked. (Go check all your tales that feature Sasha Merlo. The majority of them have new comments by yours truly.)</p>
<p>There is more I want to say but it will have to wait until I have done some of my responsibilities for today.</p>

