<blockquote>
<p>George Merlo</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Excuse you, his name is Gabe Merlo and he is the head accountant for Site-64! &gt;:V</p>
<p>In all seriousness, this was an excellent tale and a wonderful dive into Phineas's backstory, who is admittedly one of the less developed characters of TTP and the AR arc. I really appreciate the detail you put into fleshing him out as well as the excellent callback to his days as a hippy.</p>
<p>I fully consider this canon to TTP and am glad for its inclusion on the site.</p>
<p>Well done, Darkstuff. Well done.</p>

