			<div class="content" id="post-content-4856948">
									

<p>Keep the tag on the WWS tales, my dude.</p>
<p>It makes the canon much more lived in, and doesn't hurt anything. It also serves as a great intro to stuff going on within Site-64's jurisdiction that isn't directly adjacent to Site-64. I don't find the discrepancy there bothersome at all.</p>
<p>That said, if you, as the author want to remove them, that is well within your purview to do so.</p>

