<p>;-; Well, if you don't find the discrepancy bothersome, then my reason for pulling them off is nullified. If I wanted to take them off the hub whether you told me to or not I would've done it already, so rest assured that hearing your voice on this soothes my worries. Thanks for making such a fleshed out canon, and such fleshed out characters, for me to write in, and for me to put through AI isolation~!</p>

